review_details: I was wondering if this was the Olivers antiques that was in Brighton in 1950's.....i have a feeling this is just a coincidence that there is another shop of the same name?

reviewTitle: super nice captain....great afternoon of fun fishing
review_details: small fish but funny....try to catch some whilst eating dinner in the bay.....was fun as people snorkeling could see fish being caught. great crew.
